Text:
Thanks for the share.

The series use to be pretty good, but now its just an excuse of a bad series. They are starting to act bad and the special effects are pretty bad, many times you see that a whole scene is just generated on computer. I liked this series but I have lost interest, sadly.
Thankyou VTV! Warehouse 13 is probably this summers best TV show. In a lot of other shows there are too much blood, lies, betrayal and violence.
I feel the show is going down too.

I think the writers have changed.

There for awhile the Pete/Myka interactions were priceless. (Huge Myka crush, hnngh) But it seems since the end of the Sykes story arc it's kind of meh'd out. Hopefully it'll pick back up and whichever writers were responsible for late S2's and S3's near perfection will get the reigns again.
I second you Urvek. btw, a/10 v/10
I third the comments above, thanks for the upload.
